      • equals

        public boolean equals(java.lang.Object obj)
        Children of this class are used in Set collections in other code. As such, the equals method needs to be overriden to denote whether the slots have identical meaning despite being different instances. IMPORTANT: This particular implementation of the method is strictly required in the @LeafBox and @ParameterSlot classes.

        equals in class java.lang.Object
